<!DOCTYPE html>

<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>List of Rappers with the Worst Lyrics</title>
  <meta name="description" content="List of rappers with the worst rap lyrics in no particular order.">
  <meta property="og:title" content="Rappers with the Worst Lyrics" />
  <meta property="og:description" content="Discover a constanly growing list of rappers who have the worst lyrics to date" />
  <meta property="og:type" content="website" />
  <meta property="og:url" content="https://badrapapi.com/artists" />
  <link rel="canonical" href="https://badrapapi.com/artists" />
  <!-- CSS only -->
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-1BmE4kWBq78iYhFldvKuhfTAU6auU8tT94WrHftjDbrCEXSU1oBoqyl2QvZ6jIW3" crossorigin="anonymous" />
  <!-- JavaScript Bundle with Popper -->
  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-ka7Sk0Gln4gmtz2MlQnikT1wXgYsOg+OMhuP+IlRH9sENBO0LRn5q+8nbTov4+1p" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</head>

<body>
  <%- include('./navbar'); %>
  <div class="container">
    <h1 class="mt-3">Supported artists</h1>
    <p>Sort through all the rappers currently stored in the database. The list  is alphabetized and shows how many lyrics are stored for each artist.</p>
    <p>
      <% if(most_lyrics.length > 1) { %>
      <% if(most_lyrics.length == 2) { %>
    <p>Currently <b><code><%= most_lyrics[0] %></code> </b>and <b><code><%= most_lyrics[1] %></code></b> have the most bad lyrics</p>
    <% } else { %>
    Currently
    <% for(var i=0; i<most_lyrics.length; ++i) { %>
    <% if(i == most_lyrics.length-1 ) { %>
    and <b><code><%= most_lyrics[i] %></code></b>
    <% } else { %>
    <b><code><%= most_lyrics[i] %></code></b>,
    <% } %>
    <% } %>
    have the most bad lyrics stored
    <% } %>
    <% } else if(most_lyrics.length == 1) { %>
    Currently <b><code><%= most_lyrics[0] %></code></b> has the most bad lyrics stored
    <% } %>
    </p>
    <hr>
    <p><b><%= artist_data.length %> artists total</b></p>
    <div style='margin-bottom: 25px;'>
      <% for(var i=0; i<artist_data.length; ++i) { %>
      <span style='display: block;'><a href='<%= artist_data[i].artist_href %>'><%= artist_data[i].artist_name %></a> (<%= artist_data[i].artist_num_of_songs %>)</span>
      <% } %>
    </div>
    <div class="text-center" style='font-size: 10px; margin-bottom: 50px; margin-top: 50px;'>Icons made by <a href="https://www.flaticon.com/authors/sumberrejeki" title="SumberRejeki">SumberRejeki</a> from <a href="https://www.flaticon.com/" title="Flaticon">www.flaticon.com</a></div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>